Gold Futures Rebound in New York, Rising to All-Time High $1,498 an Ounce

-- B y   S t e v e   S t r o t h
-- 
2011-04-18T13:12:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-18/gold-futures-rebound-in-new-york-rising-to-all-time-high-1-498-an-ounce.html
Gold rebounded in  New York ,
touching a record $1,498 an ounce. Futures for June delivery
advanced $9.90, or 0.7 percent, to $1,495.90 at 9:11 a.m. on the
Comex. Earlier, the contract dropped as much as 0.6 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steve Stroth at 
 sstroth@bloomberg.net  